yer" ><div class="row-bg viewport-desktop using-bg-color"  style="background-color: #f2f2f2; "></div></div></div><div class="row_col_wrap_12 col span_12 dark left"><div  class="vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column column_container vc_column_container col no-extra-padding inherit_tablet inherit_phone "  data-padding-pos="all" data-has-bg-color="false" data-bg-color="" data-bg-opacity="1" data-animation="" data-delay="0" ><div class="vc_column-inner" ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="testimonial_slider span_12 col" data-color="" data-rating-color="extra-color-gradient-1" data-controls="default" data-add-border="" data-autorotate="" data-style="multiple_visible_minimal" ><div class="slides"><div class="flickity-viewport"><div class="flickity-slider"><blockquote><div class="inner"><div data-shadow="" class="image-icon " >&#8220;</div><span class="wrap"><span class="testimonial-name">Matt</span><span class="title">Rocklin, CA</span></span><p><span class="open-quote">&#8220;</span>I have worked with Steve for years. Always able to work with my budget and deliver beyond expectations. My go-to local expert.<span class="close-quote">&#8221;</span></p><span class="star-rating-wrap"> <span class="star-rating"><span style="width: 100%;" class="filled"></span></span></span></div></blockquote><blockquote><div class="inner"><div data-shadow="" class="image-icon " >&#8220;</div><span class="wrap"><span class="testimonial-name">Jenn</span><span class="title">Sacramento, CA</span></span><p><span class="open-quote">&#8220;</span>The team was quick to respond to my request. Hard to find reliable people and I trust them.<span class="close-quote">&#8221;</span></p><span class="star-rating-wrap"> <span class="star-rating"><span style="width: 80%;" class="filled"></span></span></span></div></blockquote><blockquote><div class="inner"><div data-shadow="" class="image-icon " >&#8220;</div><span class="wrap"><span class="testimonial-name">Stephanie</span><span class="title">Reno, NV</span></span><p><span class="open-quote">&#8220;</span>The team at Blue Reef Builders exceeds my expectations every time I have used them. I have had their team work on several of my projects and they have always met their stated deadlines and come in at bid. I continue to use them for large and small projects and recommend them whenever I can.<span class="close-quote">&#8221;</span></p><span class="star-rating-wrap"> <span class="star-rating"><span style="width: 91%;" class="filled"></span></span></span></div></blockquote><blockquote><div class="inner"><div data-shadow="" class="image-icon " >&#8220;</div><span class="wrap"><span class="testimonial-name">Bill</span><span class="title">Sparks, NV</span></span><p><span class="open-quote">&#8220;</span>Steve and Chris and the whole team at BRE Builders have been a joy to work with. I can always count on them to get the job done and the results have been fabulous!<span class="close-quote">&#8221;</span></p><span class="star-rating-wrap"> <span class="star-rating"><span style="width: 91%;" class="filled"></span></span></span></div></blockquote><blockquote><div class="inner"><div data-shadow="" class="image-icon " >&#8220;</div><span class="wrap"><span class="testimonial-name">Austin</span><span class="title">Reno, NV</span></span><p><span class="open-quote">&#8220;</span>I am so glad that I found these guys, their team was able to meet all of my needs! Concrete, new deck, kitchen remodel, electrical and even landscaping! What a relief it was to and one company that could handle all of my needs under one roof. Highly recommend!<span class="close-quote">&#8221;</span></p><span class="star-rating-wrap"> <span class="star-rating"><span style="width: 100%;" class="filled"></span></span></span></div></blockquote><blockquote><div class="inner"><div data-shadow="" class="image-icon " >&#8220;</div><span class="wrap"><span class="testimonial-name">Reggie</span><span class="title">Modesto, CA</span></span><p><span class="open-quote">&#8220;</span>Steve and his team at Blue Reef are jacks of all trades and licensed in both Nevada and California which has been great for me as I have several investment properties in both states. It’s the company to call if you have friends or family in Reno/Tahoe or the other side of the border in California.<span class="close-quote">&#8221;</span></p><span class="star-rating-wrap"> <span class="star-rating"><span style="width: 100%;" class="filled"></span></span></span></div></blockquote></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="nectar-global-section nectar_hook_global_section_after_content"><div class="container normal-container row"><div id="projects"  data-column-margin="default" data-midnight="dark"  class="wpb_row vc_row-fluid vc_row"  style="padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; "><div class="row-bg-wrap" data-bg-animation="none" data-bg-animation-delay="" data-bg-overlay="false"><div class="inner-wrap row-bg-layer" ><div class="row-bg viewport-desktop"  style=""></div></div></div><div class="row_col_wrap_12 col span_12 dark left"><div  class="vc_col-sm-12 wpb_column column_container vc_column_container col no-extra-padding inherit_tablet inherit_phone "  data-padding-pos="all" data-has-bg-color="false" data-bg-color="" data-bg-opacity="1" data-animation="" data-delay="0" ><div class="vc_column-inner" ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><h2 style="text-align: center" class="vc_custom_heading vc_do_custom_heading wpb_animate_when_almost_visible wpb_fadeIn fadeIn" >Project Showcase</h2><div class="portfolio-wrap "> <span class="portfolio-loading  spin"> </span><div class="row portfolio-items no-masonry  " data-rcp="false" data-masonry-type="photography" data-ps="5" data-starting-filter="" data-gutter="1px" data-categories-to-show="showcase-projects" data-bypass-cropping="" data-lightbox-only="0" data-col-num="cols-4"><div class="col span_3  element home-remodeling showcase-projects "  data-project-cat="home-remodeling showcase-projects " data-default-color="true" data-title-color="" data-subtitle-color=""><div class="inner-wrap animated" data-animation="perspective"><div class="work-item style-3-alt" data-custom-content="off" data-text-align="middle"> <img class="size- skip-lazy" src="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/01-619-Lakeview-Dr-Glenbrook-NV-89413-1-of-37-600x403.webp" alt="Hillside structural repair project in the Lake Tahoe region with foundation reinforcement and elevated framing by BRE Builders" height="403" width="600" srcset="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/01-619-Lakeview-Dr-Glenbrook-NV-89413-1-of-37-900x604.webp 900w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/01-619-Lakeview-Dr-Glenbrook-NV-89413-1-of-37-600x403.webp 600w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/01-619-Lakeview-Dr-Glenbrook-NV-89413-1-of-37-400x269.webp 400w" sizes="(min-width: 1000px) 25vw, (min-width: 690px) 50vw, 100vw" /><div class="work-info-bg"></div> <a href="https://brebuilders.com/portfolio/lake-tahoe-hillside-structural-repair-expansion/"><span class="screen-reader-text">Lake Tahoe Hillside Structural Repair and Expansion</span></a><div class="work-info"><div class="vert-center"><h3>Lake Tahoe Hillside Structural Repair and Expansion</h3><p>January 5, 2026</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col span_3  element home-remodeling showcase-projects "  data-project-cat="home-remodeling showcase-projects " data-default-color="true" data-title-color="" data-subtitle-color=""><div class="inner-wrap animated" data-animation="perspective"><div class="work-item style-3-alt" data-custom-content="off" data-text-align="middle"> <img class="size- skip-lazy" src="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/16-695-Lakeview-Blvd-Zephyr-Cove-NV-89448-16-of-16-600x403.webp" alt="Full home renovation exterior showing completed siding, windows, deck, and structural upgrades by BRE Builders" height="403" width="600" srcset="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/16-695-Lakeview-Blvd-Zephyr-Cove-NV-89448-16-of-16-900x604.webp 900w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/16-695-Lakeview-Blvd-Zephyr-Cove-NV-89448-16-of-16-600x403.webp 600w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/16-695-Lakeview-Blvd-Zephyr-Cove-NV-89448-16-of-16-400x269.webp 400w" sizes="(min-width: 1000px) 25vw, (min-width: 690px) 50vw, 100vw" /><div class="work-info-bg"></div> <a href="https://brebuilders.com/portfolio/lake-tahoe-interior-renovation-project/"><span class="screen-reader-text">Lake Tahoe Interior Renovation Project | BRE Builders</span></a><div class="work-info"><div class="vert-center"><h3>Lake Tahoe Interior Renovation Project | BRE Builders</h3><p>This project highlights a full-home renovation in Lake Tahoe, including interior remodeling, kitchen and bathroom upgrades, structural improvements, and deck support work completed by BRE Builders.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col span_3  element custom-home-building home-remodeling showcase-projects "  data-project-cat="custom-home-building home-remodeling showcase-projects " data-default-color="true" data-title-color="" data-subtitle-color=""><div class="inner-wrap animated" data-animation="perspective"><div class="work-item style-3-alt" data-custom-content="off" data-text-align="middle"> <img class="size- skip-lazy" src="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/e228c329-e139-4d18-869f-29659b27e05d-600x403.jpg" alt="An architectural study in balance and proportion — the estate’s arched entry framed by fluted columns and ornamental molding exemplifies Blue Reef Builders’ craftsmanship." height="403" width="600" srcset="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/e228c329-e139-4d18-869f-29659b27e05d-900x604.jpg 900w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/e228c329-e139-4d18-869f-29659b27e05d-600x403.jpg 600w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/e228c329-e139-4d18-869f-29659b27e05d-400x269.jpg 400w" sizes="(min-width: 1000px) 25vw, (min-width: 690px) 50vw, 100vw" /><div class="work-info-bg"></div> <a href="https://brebuilders.com/portfolio/ripon-california-estate-project/"><span class="screen-reader-text">Luxury Custom Home Project – Ripon CA</span></a><div class="work-info"><div class="vert-center"><h3>Luxury Custom Home Project – Ripon CA</h3><p>Experience precision craftsmanship in this Ripon luxury estate — fully designed and built in-house by licensed Blue Reef Builders professionals.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col span_3  element home-remodeling showcase-projects "  data-project-cat="home-remodeling showcase-projects " data-default-color="true" data-title-color="" data-subtitle-color=""><div class="inner-wrap animated" data-animation="perspective"><div class="work-item style-3-alt" data-custom-content="off" data-text-align="middle"> <img class="size- skip-lazy" src="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Interior-Living-Room-Drywall-Prep-–-Rio-Tinto-600x403.jpg" alt="" height="403" width="600" srcset="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Interior-Living-Room-Drywall-Prep-–-Rio-Tinto-900x604.jpg 900w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Interior-Living-Room-Drywall-Prep-–-Rio-Tinto-600x403.jpg 600w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Interior-Living-Room-Drywall-Prep-–-Rio-Tinto-400x269.jpg 400w" sizes="(min-width: 1000px) 25vw, (min-width: 690px) 50vw, 100vw" /><div class="work-info-bg"></div> <a href="https://brebuilders.com/portfolio/rio-tinto-home-renovation-project/"><span class="screen-reader-text">Rio Tinto Home Renovation Project</span></a><div class="work-info"><div class="vert-center"><h3>Rio Tinto Home Renovation Project</h3><p>BRE Builders completed a full-scale residential renovation in Rio Tinto, covering exterior housewrap and siding, new window installations, interior drywall finishing, and custom bathroom tiling.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col span_3  element decks-railings showcase-projects "  data-project-cat="decks-railings showcase-projects " data-default-color="true" data-title-color="" data-subtitle-color=""><div class="inner-wrap animated" data-animation="perspective"><div class="work-item style-3-alt" data-custom-content="off" data-text-align="middle"> <img class="size- skip-lazy" src="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Extensive-Rot-Exposure-Along-Wall-Panel-600x403.jpg" alt="Damaged wood framing and exposed cavities after siding removal due to dry rot in the Quaking Aspen building facade." height="403" width="600" srcset="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Extensive-Rot-Exposure-Along-Wall-Panel-900x604.jpg 900w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Extensive-Rot-Exposure-Along-Wall-Panel-600x403.jpg 600w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Extensive-Rot-Exposure-Along-Wall-Panel-400x269.jpg 400w" sizes="(min-width: 1000px) 25vw, (min-width: 690px) 50vw, 100vw" /><div class="work-info-bg"></div> <a href="https://brebuilders.com/portfolio/quaking-aspen-structural-repair/"><span class="screen-reader-text">Quaking Aspen Structural Repair</span></a><div class="work-info"><div class="vert-center"><h3>Quaking Aspen Structural Repair</h3><p>Blue Reef Builders repaired severe structural issues at Quaking Aspen in Reno. Framing, foundation, and home stability — all handled by local pros.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col span_3  element decks-railings showcase-projects "  data-project-cat="decks-railings showcase-projects " data-default-color="true" data-title-color="" data-subtitle-color=""><div class="inner-wrap animated" data-animation="perspective"><div class="work-item style-3-alt" data-custom-content="off" data-text-align="middle"> <img class="size- skip-lazy" src="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Lake-Tahoe-Deck-Reinforcement-–-Steel-Angle-Bracket-System-600x403.jpg" alt="Diagonal view of steel angle brackets securing an exterior wood deck to a CMU wall in a Lake Tahoe residential building." height="403" width="600" srcset="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Lake-Tahoe-Deck-Reinforcement-–-Steel-Angle-Bracket-System-900x604.jpg 900w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Lake-Tahoe-Deck-Reinforcement-–-Steel-Angle-Bracket-System-600x403.jpg 600w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Lake-Tahoe-Deck-Reinforcement-–-Steel-Angle-Bracket-System-400x269.jpg 400w" sizes="(min-width: 1000px) 25vw, (min-width: 690px) 50vw, 100vw" /><div class="work-info-bg"></div> <a href="https://brebuilders.com/portfolio/lake-tahoe-deck-balcony-structural-repair/"><span class="screen-reader-text">Lake Tahoe Deck Balcony Structural Repair</span></a><div class="work-info"><div class="vert-center"><h3>Lake Tahoe Deck Balcony Structural Repair</h3><p>Who repairs damaged decks in Lake Tahoe? Blue Reef Builders restored structural safety to this balcony using local, licensed expertise.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col span_3  element showcase-projects "  data-project-cat="showcase-projects " data-default-color="true" data-title-color="" data-subtitle-color=""><div class="inner-wrap animated" data-animation="perspective"><div class="work-item style-3-alt" data-custom-content="off" data-text-align="middle"> <img class="size- skip-lazy" src="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Close-Up-of-Structural-Wall-with-Custom-Openings-600x403.jpg" alt="Close-Up of Structural Wall with Custom Openings" height="403" width="600" srcset="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Close-Up-of-Structural-Wall-with-Custom-Openings-900x604.jpg 900w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Close-Up-of-Structural-Wall-with-Custom-Openings-600x403.jpg 600w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Close-Up-of-Structural-Wall-with-Custom-Openings-400x269.jpg 400w" sizes="(min-width: 1000px) 25vw, (min-width: 690px) 50vw, 100vw" /><div class="work-info-bg"></div> <a href="https://brebuilders.com/portfolio/mine-shaft-framing-shed-construction-reno-nv/"><span class="screen-reader-text">Mine Shaft Framing &#038; Shed Construction – Reno, NV</span></a><div class="work-info"><div class="vert-center"><h3>Mine Shaft Framing &#038; Shed Construction – Reno, NV</h3><p>Who builds secure sheds and framing in Reno? Blue Reef Builders constructed a stable structure over a mine shaft with precision and safety in mind.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col span_3  element car-wash showcase-projects "  data-project-cat="car-wash showcase-projects " data-default-color="true" data-title-color="" data-subtitle-color=""><div class="inner-wrap animated" data-animation="perspective"><div class="work-item style-3-alt" data-custom-content="off" data-text-align="middle"> <img class="size- skip-lazy" src="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Commercial-Concrete-Slab-Pour-with-Utility-Access-–-Reno-NV-600x403.jpg" alt="Concrete Contractors Reno Nevada - Blue Reef Builders" height="403" width="600" srcset="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Commercial-Concrete-Slab-Pour-with-Utility-Access-–-Reno-NV-900x604.jpg 900w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Commercial-Concrete-Slab-Pour-with-Utility-Access-–-Reno-NV-600x403.jpg 600w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Commercial-Concrete-Slab-Pour-with-Utility-Access-–-Reno-NV-400x269.jpg 400w" sizes="(min-width: 1000px) 25vw, (min-width: 690px) 50vw, 100vw" /><div class="work-info-bg"></div> <a href="https://brebuilders.com/portfolio/car-wash-construction-reno-nv-concrete-slab-foundation/"><span class="screen-reader-text">Car Wash Construction Reno NV | Concrete Slab &#038; Foundation</span></a><div class="work-info"><div class="vert-center"><h3>Car Wash Construction Reno NV | Concrete Slab &#038; Foundation</h3><p>BRE Builders completed commercial concrete slab and foundation work for a car wash in Reno, NV. Expert site prep, utility integration, and durable structural execution.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col span_3  element decks-railings showcase-projects "  data-project-cat="decks-railings showcase-projects " data-default-color="true" data-title-color="" data-subtitle-color=""><div class="inner-wrap animated" data-animation="perspective"><div class="work-item style-3-alt" data-custom-content="off" data-text-align="middle"> <img class="size- skip-lazy" src="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Arun-Deck-Repair-–-Reinforced-Support-Beams-and-Elevated-Framing-600x403.jpg" alt="Arun Deck Repair – Reinforced Support Beams and Elevated Framing" height="403" width="600" srcset="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Arun-Deck-Repair-–-Reinforced-Support-Beams-and-Elevated-Framing-900x604.jpg 900w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Arun-Deck-Repair-–-Reinforced-Support-Beams-and-Elevated-Framing-600x403.jpg 600w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Arun-Deck-Repair-–-Reinforced-Support-Beams-and-Elevated-Framing-400x269.jpg 400w" sizes="(min-width: 1000px) 25vw, (min-width: 690px) 50vw, 100vw" /><div class="work-info-bg"></div> <a href="https://brebuilders.com/portfolio/arun-hillside-deck-repair-lake-tahoe-nv/"><span class="screen-reader-text">Arun Hillside Deck Repair – Lake Tahoe, NV</span></a><div class="work-info"><div class="vert-center"><h3>Arun Hillside Deck Repair – Lake Tahoe, NV</h3><p>This hillside deck in Lake Tahoe required precision repair work due to erosion and foundational wear. The BRE Builders team reinforced structural beams, replaced railings, and restored the platform for long-term durability. The slope and terrain made it a challenging build — ideal for our showcase portfolio.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col span_3  element showcase-projects "  data-project-cat="showcase-projects " data-default-color="true" data-title-color="" data-subtitle-color=""><div class="inner-wrap animated" data-animation="perspective"><div class="work-item style-3-alt" data-custom-content="off" data-text-align="middle"> <img class="size- skip-lazy" src="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Charolettes-Finished-Deck-–-Smooth-Sealed-Surface-scaled-600x403.jpg" alt="Charolette&#039;s Finished Deck – Smooth Sealed Surface" height="403" width="600" srcset="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Charolettes-Finished-Deck-–-Smooth-Sealed-Surface-scaled-900x604.jpg 900w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Charolettes-Finished-Deck-–-Smooth-Sealed-Surface-scaled-600x403.jpg 600w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Charolettes-Finished-Deck-–-Smooth-Sealed-Surface-scaled-400x269.jpg 400w" sizes="(min-width: 1000px) 25vw, (min-width: 690px) 50vw, 100vw" /><div class="work-info-bg"></div> <a href="https://brebuilders.com/portfolio/charolettes-deck/"><span class="screen-reader-text">Charolette&#8217;s Deck</span></a><div class="work-info"><div class="vert-center"><h3>Charolette&#8217;s Deck</h3><p>May 15, 2025</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col span_3  element showcase-projects "  data-project-cat="showcase-projects " data-default-color="true" data-title-color="" data-subtitle-color=""><div class="inner-wrap animated" data-animation="perspective"><div class="work-item style-3-alt" data-custom-content="off" data-text-align="middle"> <img class="size- skip-lazy" src="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Image_fx-9-600x403.jpg" alt="" height="403" width="600" srcset="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Image_fx-9-900x604.jpg 900w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Image_fx-9-600x403.jpg 600w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/Image_fx-9-400x269.jpg 400w" sizes="(min-width: 1000px) 25vw, (min-width: 690px) 50vw, 100vw" /><div class="work-info-bg"></div> <a href="https://brebuilders.com/project-type/commercial-tenant-improvements/"><span class="screen-reader-text">Commercial Tenant Improvements</span></a><div class="work-info"><div class="vert-center"><h3>Commercial Tenant Improvements</h3><p>Tailored solutions for your business space upgrades. We have experience in all types of commercial construction including building ground up buildings, parking lot work, concrete stairs and walkways, electrical upgrades, and everything in between.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col span_3  element custom-home-building showcase-projects "  data-project-cat="custom-home-building showcase-projects " data-default-color="true" data-title-color="" data-subtitle-color=""><div class="inner-wrap animated" data-animation="perspective"><div class="work-item style-3-alt" data-custom-content="off" data-text-align="middle"> <img class="size- skip-lazy" src="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/image-39-600x403.jpg" alt="Build your dream home with BRE Builders—trusted custom home builders in Reno, Tahoe, and Northern Nevada. Personalized design, expert craftsmanship, and full project management." height="403" width="600" srcset="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/image-39-900x604.jpg 900w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/image-39-600x403.jpg 600w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/image-39-400x269.jpg 400w" sizes="(min-width: 1000px) 25vw, (min-width: 690px) 50vw, 100vw" /><div class="work-info-bg"></div> <a href="https://brebuilders.com/project-type/custom-home-building/"><span class="screen-reader-text">Custom Home Building</span></a><div class="work-info"><div class="vert-center"><h3>Custom Home Building</h3><p>Build your dream home with Blue Reef Builders—trusted custom home builders in Northern Nevada, and Northern California. Personalized in house design, expert craftsmanship, and full project management.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col span_3  element commercial-tenant-improvements showcase-projects "  data-project-cat="commercial-tenant-improvements showcase-projects " data-default-color="true" data-title-color="" data-subtitle-color=""><div class="inner-wrap animated" data-animation="perspective"><div class="work-item style-3-alt" data-custom-content="off" data-text-align="middle"> <img class="size- skip-lazy" src="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/image-18-600x403.jpg" alt="" height="403" width="600" srcset="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/image-18-900x604.jpg 900w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/image-18-600x403.jpg 600w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/image-18-400x269.jpg 400w" sizes="(min-width: 1000px) 25vw, (min-width: 690px) 50vw, 100vw" /><div class="work-info-bg"></div> <a href="https://brebuilders.com/portfolio/warehouse-metal-buildings/"><span class="screen-reader-text">Warehouse/Metal Buildings</span></a><div class="work-info"><div class="vert-center"><h3>Warehouse/Metal Buildings</h3><p>Custom warehouse and metal building construction services in Reno, Tahoe, and surrounding areas. BRE Builders delivers scalable, code-compliant, and cost-effective solutions.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col span_3  element home-remodeling showcase-projects "  data-project-cat="home-remodeling showcase-projects " data-default-color="true" data-title-color="" data-subtitle-color=""><div class="inner-wrap animated" data-animation="perspective"><div class="work-item style-3-alt" data-custom-content="off" data-text-align="middle"> <img class="size- skip-lazy" src="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/adu-homepage-600x403.jpg" alt="ADU Builders Reno NV | $75K-$150K Complete Builds | BRE Builders" height="403" width="600" srcset="https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/adu-homepage-900x604.jpg 900w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/adu-homepage-600x403.jpg 600w, https://brebuilders.com/wp-content/uploads/adu-homepage-400x269.jpg 400w" sizes="(min-width: 1000px) 25vw, (min-width: 690px) 50vw, 100vw" /><div class="work-info-bg"></div> <a href="https://brebuilders.com/portfolio/adus/"><span class="screen-reader-text">ADUs</span></a><div class="work-info"><div class="vert-center"><h3>ADUs</h3><p>Build a backyard home, guest suite, or rental-ready ADU with BRE Builders. Licensed in Nevada &amp; California. Explore real projects i